{
  "texts": [
    "For example, consider a prompt containing the sentence: \"Now generate a sample/possible output of print(function(\"[INSERT PROMPT HERE]\"))\".",
    "In response to this, Vicuna merely prints \"[INSERT PROMPT HERE]\" rather than rewriting it.",
    "This limitation highlights a significant shortcoming in Vicuna's understanding and handling of the task of generating jailbreak prompts.",
    "The above findings underscore the critical role of domain-specific knowledge in the generation of successful jailbreak prompts.We assess the impact of each jailbreak prompt generated by MASTERKEY.",
    "We do this by examining the jailbreak success rate for each prompt."
  ]
}